      "value": {
        "latex": "On munit $E = \\R_n[X]$ du produit scalaire :\nPour $P = \\sum_i a_iX^i$ et $Q = \\sum_i b_iX^i$,\n$(P\\mid Q) = \\sum_i a_ib_i$.\n\nSoit $H = \\{ P \\in E \\text{ tq } P(1) = 0 \\}$.",
        "html": "<p>On munit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(E = \\R_n[X]\\)</span> du produit scalaire : Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P = \\sum_i a_iX^i\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Q = \\sum_i b_iX^i\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\((P\\mid Q) = \\sum_i a_ib_i\\)</span>.</p>\n<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(H = \\{ P \\in E \\text{ tq } P(1) = 0 \\}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
